      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RED ROCK BLOOM (8) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (18.53) at this track behind Moses Magic in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Top prospect. ASTON JOE (2) comes off an average run last start when fifth at this track over 318m behind Zoe's Secret (19.05) in a Grade 4/5. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expected to run well. ONE NUMBER AWAY (1) last appeared when too good (21.23) over 340m at Gunnedah on March 18. Resumes after finishing eighth (21.23) at Gunnedah over 340m three-and-a-half months ago. Tends to go well off this box draw. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. LUMEAH MATILDA (4) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
